  <div class="bg-sand rounded-xl p-6 my-8 not-prose">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-sm">
      <div><h4 class="font-semibold text-anthracite mb-2">Trailhead Parking</h4><p class="text-anthracite-light">Several designated car parks serve as starting points. See our <a href="/en/discover/map/" class="text-ith-blue">interactive map</a>.</p></div>
      <div><h4 class="font-semibold text-anthracite mb-2">Digital Maps</h4><p class="text-anthracite-light">All routes are available on Komoot and Outdooractive. GPS tracks can be downloaded.</p></div>
      <div><h4 class="font-semibold text-anthracite mb-2">Rest Stops</h4><p class="text-anthracite-light">Rest areas, shelters and dining options are available along the trails.</p></div>
      <div><h4 class="font-semibold text-anthracite mb-2">Best Season</h4><p class="text-anthracite-light">Open year-round. Especially recommended in spring (blossoms) and autumn (foliage). Winter hiking also possible.</p></div>
